Vehement:


The Archbishop nodded as Destructor and his forces put down their weapons.  
Forty-five?  Doubtful Vehement thought.

"We shall wait for KitKat.  I would invite you inside, but we were attacked 
by Maximals on our way here, and suffered damage to our ship.  Currently 
deadly gases are leaking through the ship, my forces are trying to clean 
them.  Or so I'm told, but I'm not mechanic."

"Have you ever heard of a Predacon named Koga Shuko, or a Predacon named Set?"
